 \\"},{\\"id\\":\\"19db042b55d83e55\\",\\"threadId\\":\\"19db042b55d83e55\\",\\"snippet\\":\\"AI Enthusiasts skool logo 1 new notification Since 8:37 pm (Apr 21, 2026) Here's what you missed: Krystian Wojtarowicz (following) posted: Most people are still building PowerPoints manually…\\",\\"payload\\":{\\"mimeType\\":\\"multipart/alternative\\"},\\"sizeEstimate\\":70351,\\"historyId\\":\\"3021096\\",\\"internalDate\\":\\"1776778652000\\",\\"labels\\":[{\\"id\\":\\"INBOX\\",\\"name\\":\\"INBOX\\"},{\\"id\\":\\"CATEGORY_UPDATES\\",\\"name\\":\\"CATEGORY_UPDATES\\"},{\\"id\\":\\"UNREAD\\",\\"name\\":\\"UNREAD\\"}],\\"From\\":\\"\\\\\\"AI Enthusiasts (Skool)\\\\\\" <noreply@skool.com>\\",\\"Subject\\":\\"1 new notification since 8:37 pm (Apr 21, 2026)\\",\\"To\\":\\"Freyan Bambics <amberbambico.54@gmail.com>\\"}]",{"lc":1,"type":"693","id":"694"},"llama-3.1-8b-instant",{"lc":1,"type":"695","id":"696","kwargs":"697"},{"lc":1,"type":"695","id":"698","kwargs":"699"},{"lc":1,"type":"695","id":"700","kwargs":"701"},{"lc":1,"type":"695","id":"702","kwargs":"703"},{"lc":1,"type":"695","id":"704","kwargs":"705"},{"lc":1,"type":"695","id":"706","kwargs":"707"},{"lc":1,"type":"695","id":"708","kwargs":"709"},{"lc":1,"type":"695","id":"710","kwargs":"711"},{"lc":1,"type":"695","id":"712","kwargs":"713"},{"lc":1,"type":"695","id":"714","kwargs":"715"},{"lc":1,"type":"695","id":"716","kwargs":"717"},{"lc":1,"type":"695","id":"718","kwargs":"719"},["720"],"System: You are a helpful assistant\\nHuman: what is the capital of thailand?\\nAI: The capital of Thailand is Bangkok.\\nHuman: how much would it take if i want to go on vacation there?\\nAI: The cost of a vacation in Bangkok, Thailand can vary greatly depending on several factors such as the time of year, accommodation options, and personal spending habits. However, here are some estimated costs to help you plan:\\n\\n1. Flights:\\n    1. **Round-trip flights from the US**: $800-$1,200\\n    2. **Round-trip flights from Europe**: $600-$1,000\\n    3. **Round-trip flights from Australia**: $400-$800\\n2. Accommodation:\\n    1. **Hostel dorm**: $10-$20 per night\\n    2. **Budget hotel**: $20-$40 per night\\n    3. **Mid-range hotel**: $40-$80 per night\\n    4. **Luxury hotel**: $150-$300 per night\\n3. Food:\\n    1. **Street food**: $3-$5 per meal\\n    2. **Mid-range restaurant**: $10-$20 per meal\\n    3. **Fine dining**: $30-$50 per meal\\n4. Transportation:\\n    1. **Taxi ride**: $5-$10\\n    2. **Tuk-tuk ride**: $10-$20\\n    3. **Public transportation**: $1-$3\\n5. Attractions:\\n    1. **Temple entrance fees**: $5-$10\\n    2. **Museum entrance fees**: $10-$20\\n    3. **Guided tours**: $50-$100\\n\\nOverall, a budget-conscious traveler could expect to spend around $30-$50 per day, while a mid-range traveler could spend around $80-$120 per day. Luxury travelers could spend $200-$500 per day or more.\\n\\nFor a 7-day trip to Bangkok, here are some estimated total costs:\\n\\n1. **Budget**: $1,000-$1,500\\n2. **Mid-range**: $1,500-$2,500\\n3. **Luxury**: $3,000-$5,000\\n\\nKeep in mind that these are just estimates, and your actual costs may vary depending on your specific travel plans and preferences.\\nHuman: hello\\nAI: Hello. Is there anything else I can help you with or would you like to continue planning your trip to Bangkok?\\nHuman: can you give me the list of the unread emails today?",{"lc":1,"type":"693","id":"721"},"multipart/alternative",{"id":"722","name":"722"},{"id":"723","name":"723"},{"id":"724","name":"724"},{"id":"725","name":"725"},{"id":"726","name":"726"},"text/html","secret",["727"],"constructor",["728","729","730"],{"content":"731","additional_kwargs":"732","response_metadata":"733"},["728","729","734"],{"content":"735","tool_calls":"736","invalid_tool_calls":"737","additional_kwargs":"738","response_metadata":"739"},["728","729","730"],{"content":"740","additional_kwargs":"741","response_metadata":"742"},["728","729","734"],{"content":"743","tool_calls":"744